<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690735>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal and lateral views of the lectotype of Calligrapha polyspila (Germar) (a), the holotype of C. matronalis Erichson (b), and dorsal views of the holotypes of Polypsila polyspila var. plagata Achard (c) and P. polyspila var. bilineolata Achard (d). Scale = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690739>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal (apex), ventral and lateral views of the penises of Calligrapha polyspila (Germar) (a), C. matronalis Erichson (b), C. melasomina Bechyné (c), C. multiplagata (Achard) (d), C. multiplagata cochabambana Bechyné (e), and C. billbergi Stål (f). Scale = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690741>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution of Calligrapha polyspila (Germar) (black circles) and of C. multiplagata (Achard) (white circles). Gray circles denote localities where specimens consistent with the types of C. melasomina Bechyné and C. multiplagata cochabambana Bechyné have been recorded." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4690741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

